  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>論文燃やされたからあんなこと言うなんて
やつあたりだよ……ひどい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That man said &lt;Claus&gt;'s thesis was burnt and that it made him to go mad...How cruel...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クル～～ルゥ～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、&lt;Mel&gt;が髪飾り全部捨てられたら
どうすんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When all your hair accessories were thrown away you didn't like it one bit either, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>確かに落ち込むけど、
あんなこと言わないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I got really down due to it but... that's not the same type of bad things!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>育てた鉢植えや花壇の花、
掘り返されたら？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What about the potted plant and the flower you liked so much? They withered away, remember?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それもイヤだよ、でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That was horrible too, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ポエム書いたノート、
燃やされるとか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What about the notebook you wrote your poems got burnt?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That too was...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？
なんで、&lt;Dio&gt;、そのこと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...? How do you know all these things...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール～？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kururuu?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、やべっ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, crap...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_013_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひどーいっ！！　見たの！
ちょっと！　待ちなさいっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You did all those things? You're terrible! Hold on! Wait right there!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
